\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {S1}{\ignorespaces Input-data fields for the 579 catchments. (a) Curve number (antecedent moisture condition II); (b) time of concentration; (c) 25-year design rainfall depth for a storm of duration equal to the time of concentration; (d) soil clay fraction at the catchments; (e) gridded SoilGrids 250~m clay fraction; (f) gridded 1-hour, 25-year design rainfall intensity computed from the Sherman IDF parameters. Biome (light grey) and national (dark grey) boundaries are shown.}}{4}{figure.1}%
